  "prompt": "What is a good way to say \u6a2a\u5411\u5377\u8f74rpg\u6e38\u620f in English?",
  "response": "A good English translation for \"\u6a2a\u5411\u5377\u8f74RPG\u6e38\u620f\" is:\n\n**\"Side-Scrolling RPG Game\"**\n\n**Breakdown:**\n- **Side-Scrolling**: Refers to the horizontal movement typical in games where the action moves from left to right (or vice versa) across the screen.\n- **RPG**: Stands for Role-Playing Game, a genre where players control characters and undertake quests in a fictional setting.\n\n**Alternative Phrases:**\n- **\"Side-Scroller RPG\"**\n- **\"Horizontal Scroll RPG Game\"**\n\nThese alternatives convey the same meaning and are also commonly understood in the gaming community.",
